item.title: Privacy Policy
item.dc:creator: galleriroselil.dk
item.content:encoded:
Who we are

Suggested text: Our website address is: https://www.galleriroselil.dk.

Comments

Suggested text: When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.

An anonymised string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service Privacy Policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.

Media

Suggested text: If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.

Cookies

Suggested text: If you leave a comment on our site you may opt in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.

If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select "Remember Me", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.

If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.

Embedded content from other websites

Suggested text: Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.

These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.

Who we share your data with

Suggested text: If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.

How long we retain your data

Suggested text: If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognise and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.

What rights you have over your data

Suggested text: If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.

Where we send your data

Suggested text: Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.

quizspillet

Der tager dig med p en musikalsk rejse tilbage til de strste 90'er hits!

Forhandler

Om spillet

Absolute music quizspillet, giver dig stemningen fra de glade 90'er.

Du behver ikke at vre nogen super quizmaster for at spille med og have det sjovt. Spillets playlister vil med garanti bringe dig tilbage til de gode 90'er-minder og give dig et smil p lben. Om du er verdensmester i 90'er hits eller bare elsker lyden af fortiden, s er spillet lige noget for dig!

Ls om spillet

Mrk nostalgien

Vi har gjort det nemt for dig og blandet hits fra alle 29 albums!

Bliv grebet af den gode stemning,medde festlige albumcovers spredt udover bordetog til lyden af fortidens genkendelige toner. Dyk ned i playlisterne, se musikvideoer og lad 90'er-nostalgien tage over.

Hr musikken

Quiz med p Instagram

Skal du lige have genopfrisket hukommelsen, inden du giver dig i kast med spillet - s hop ind og besg os p instagram, hvor du kan quizze med. Du finder quizzen i highlights.

Om os bag spillet

Hej vi er Astrid og Stigne fra Just good coffee thanks der str bag Absolute music quizspillet.

Vi har gang i en masse spndende og kreative projekter. Vores frste projekt hedder Evrlily, mske kender du det allerede? Evrlily er et talerr for sm selvstndige kunstnere, hvor vi slger personlige stamtrer og horoskoper. Derudover har vi en ske fuld af gode ideer, som vi bare venter p at kunne dele med dig. Er du blevet nysgerrig p Evrlily? S hop ind forbi og se alle de smukke og eventyrlige plakater.Vi ses!

Musikken

Absolute music er lyden af 90'erne. Med 29 album bag sig, er du garanteret en aften fuld af nostalgi og hits du bare m synge med p. Vi har gjort det nemt for dig og blandet alle de gode sange som du kan hre en forsmag p her.

Spotify

Hvilken Absolute music cd er din favorit?

Kan du huske den? Det farverige albumcover, billardkuglen p forsiden og din yndlingssang p repeat. Vi har lagt coveret i sken, s du kan finde den blandt de 29 spilkort.

Lyden af 90'erne

"Would I lie to you" er p en af de frste Absolute music udgivelser - hvilken?
Hint (Det er Joy mogensens favoritalbum)

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G_UXvcr22rMhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8WEtxJ4-sh4https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C-u5WLJ9Yk4

En ske fuld af nostalgi

Sammen med musikken er de ikoniske albumcovers spillets hjerte.

Bliv grebet af den gode stemning,medde festlige albumcovers.Dyk ned i playlisterne, se musikvideoer og lad 90'er nostalgien tage over - kan du mon stadig huske teksten til din yndlingssang?

forhandlere

Vi er glade for at du vil spille med!

Prcis som med CD'erne dengang, kan spillet kbes i dit lokale supermarked/butik.

Rigtig god fornjelse og husk at deltage i konkurrencen nedenfor!

    Konkurrence

    Savner du ogs 90'erne? Det gr vi! Derfor har vi stablet den fedeste konkurrence p benene i samarbejde med dit lokalevarehus.

    VIND en 90'er festpakke, der indeholder alt hvad du skal bruge, for at holde den perfekte fest for 10 personer.

    Pakken indeholder et Absolute music quizspil, og massere af lkkerier der oser af 90'er nostalgi. Alt du skal gre er at like opslaget, flge spillet og tagge 3 du nsker at inviterer med til festen!

    (Og nu du er inde forbi vores instagram, kan du jo lige prve at quizze med)

Om spillet

Absolute music quizspillet, er som at tage en tidsmaskine tilbage til de glade 90'er.

Spillet indeholder playlister med sange fra alle de 29 Absolute music albums, og bliver med garanti festens midtpunkt. Fordyb dig i de dekorative spilkort og vk minderne til live.

Forhandler

Inspiration

Spillets forside er inspireret af det bedst slgende album, Absolute music 10.

Sdan kommer du i gang

1.

Kom godt i gang og find dit Absolute music quizspil frem

2.

Spred de 29 spilkort med album coverne p ud over bordet

3.

Find playlisterne frem og s er du i gang!

Musikken

Det er bare lidt sjovere nr man er 1 2 3 4 ..

Hvilken Thomas Helmig sang var p Absolute music nr 28?

Lad Absolute musikquizzen danne rammen om din nste fest. Saml alle du kender og genoplev de glade 90'er-minder sammen.

Hr musikken

Det siger andre om spillet

Karl Ufaglrt

Det er mega sjovt og mindede mig om min frste CD.

Boris Slger

Det er virkelig svrt at sidde stille til det her spil!

Sidsel Mejerist

NOSTALGISK 90'er stemning. JEG ER VILD MED DET!!
